Hshicorp- vault
helm repo add hashicorp link
helm install vault 
go inside vault pod
when vault is initialised, it is sealed by default
vault login and enter root token

vault secrets list
vault secrets enable kv-v2

===add a new secret====

vault kv put kv-v2/vault-demo/mysecret username=shabbir
vault kv get kv-v2/vault-demo/mysecret

vault policy list 

vault policy write mysecret - << EOF
path "kv-v2/vault-demo/mysecret" {
capabilities = ["read"]
}
EOF

